### =====================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES
### =====================================================

### 1️⃣ Get Active Banners (Hero)
GET {{baseUrl}}/banners/active?type=hero
Content-Type: application/json


### 2️⃣ Track View
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/banners/69a08bb0fe18c45efe71d283/view
Content-Type: application/json


### 3️⃣ Track Click
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/banners/69a08bb0fe18c45efe71d283/click
Content-Type: application/json



### =====================================================
### ADMIN ROUTES (Require JWT)
### =====================================================

### 4️⃣ Get All Banners (Admin Table)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json



### 5️⃣ Create Banner (WITH IMAGE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Learn. Grow. Succeed.
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subtitle"

Master new skills with our comprehensive online courses
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="buttonText"

Explore Courses
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="buttonUrl"

/courses
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

hero
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isActive"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="displayOrder"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="banner.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./banner.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--



### 6️⃣ Update Banner (OPTIONAL IMAGE)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/{{bannerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Updated Banner Title
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="displayOrder"

2
------WebKitFormBoundary--



### 7️⃣ Soft Delete Banner
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/69a08bb0fe18c45efe71d283
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}



### 8️⃣ Hard Delete Banner
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/69a08bb0fe18c45efe71d283/hard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}



### 9️⃣ Toggle Active Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/69a08bb0fe18c45efe71d283/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json